perfSONAR_PS::Client::LS::Remote README File
============================================

Description
-----------

perfSONAR_PS::Client::LS::Remote is a module that provides an OO interface for
performing queries and registering data with a perfSONAR Lookup Service.


Installation
------------

 CPAN installation
 -----------------

    perl -MCPAN -e 'install perfSONAR_PS::Client::LS::Remote'

 Standard installation
 ---------------------

    Prerequisites:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

